1
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,719
You don't need to worry about Mom.

2
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:55,560
If you're still willing to go to the vinegar workshop,

3
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,560
just go ahead.

4
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:01,479
At first, I went to the vinegar workshop to pay off debt.

5
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:04,200
But later,

6
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:07,319
I really felt that Sister Yingrong is amazing.

7
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:08,920
She isn't afraid of hardship,

8
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,280
doesn't admit defeat,

9
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,359
and can handle responsibility.

10
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,239
Gradually,

11
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,920
I wanted to be with her.

12
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:19,719
You like her.

13
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,280
Does this count as liking?

14
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,920
Brother, do you also like Sister Yingrong?

15
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,319
Get up.

16
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,480
Let's have a fight.

17
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,120
Whoever wins,

18
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:55,280
Sister Yingrong belongs to him.

19
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,560
Haiyang.

20
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,719
Is there something wrong with your head?

21
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,319
Hurry up and find someone else to date.

22
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:04,959
You don't dare fight me.

23
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,359
You're afraid of losing.

24
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:16,520
Haiyang.

25
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,520
Feelings can't be settled by a fight.

26
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,800
And it's not just a problem between us two.

27
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,080
Wang Yingrong has the right to choose who she likes.

28
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,000
Besides,

29
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,719
I was the one who taught you how to fight.

30
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:34,919
Brother.

31
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,719
If Sister Yingrong likes you,

32
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:37,719
I'll give you my blessing.

33
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,960
But if you don't even dare to confess,

34
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:40,759
I won't mind

35
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:42,400
shamelessly continuing to pester her.

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,080
What brings you here?

37
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,520
I came to apologize to you on behalf of my mom.

38
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,919
I understand.

39
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:59,400
It's normal for her to worry.

40
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,719
But during this time,

41
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,639
thanks to Xiaochuan and Haiyang,

42
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,680
my vinegar workshop is where it is today.

43
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,199
Didn't I say it's unsafe,

44
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,719
and not to come here for the night watch?

45
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,280
I was still a bit worried.

46
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,199
Haiyang said he would keep watch today.

47
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,479
I saw he was too tired during the day,

48
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,560
so I told him to go back.

49
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,120
During this period,

50
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:25,360
has it just been you and Haiyang?

51
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:31,919
Just the two of you busy together?

52
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,599
Twenty-four hours a day,

53
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,919
spending eighteen hours together.

54
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,000
I see Haiyang as a younger brother.

55
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,800
In my heart, he is...

56
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,080
...just the same as Xiaochuan.

57
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,759
That's all.

58
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,879
Don't you have anything you want to say to me?

59
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,120
Say what?

60
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,759
Let me tell you.

61
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,040
I'm telling you this now...

62
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,480
...not because I like you.

63
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,279
And it's not like I have to like you.

64
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,160
Stop talking about Haiyang.

65
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,959
The people in your Zheng family...

66
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,279
...I don't think any of them are good enough.

67
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,560
Just because I said I liked you before...

68
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,240
...doesn't mean...

69
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,759
...I like you now or will in the future.

70
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,160
Women are fickle.

71
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,279
I'm so outstanding.

72
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,639
You have no idea, at the matchmaker's...

73
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:34,759
...how long the line is for me.

74
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,480
I know.

75
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,000
If I want to confess my feelings to you...

76
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,720
...what do I need to prepare?

77
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,360
Need...

78
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:53,000
You need to prepare a lot.

79
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,120
You need to prepare...

80
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:55,839
Cigarettes.

81
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:56,439
Alcohol.

82
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,040
Tea.

83
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,519
Candy.

84
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:58,120
You need The Three Golds.

85
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,639
You need home appliances.

86
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,600
You need a grand wedding procession.

87
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,399
And also...

88
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,560
And also...

89
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,600
And also one hundred love letters.

90
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,120
Need...

91
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:08,839
Need...

92
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,279
Need so much?

93
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,519
Of course.

94
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,480
Yingrong.

95
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:19,319
I have things to do, I'm going back first.

96
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,120
You should go back early too.

97
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:25,959
Zheng Minjiang.

98
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:26,920
You idiot.

99
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,720
What did you say?

100
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,519
Nothing.

101
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,040
What's wrong?

102
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,040
Your foot...

103
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,839
Move.

104
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:01,759
Need... need to prepare so much?

105
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:04,199
One hundred love letters.

106
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:20,720
I don't know if this diary counts

107
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,199
Who wants that messy stuff anyway

108
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,959
Don't you know a sincere heart

109
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,399
Am I asking for too much

110
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:29,040
I don't like you

111
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,279
Not even a little bit

112
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,879
You just play dumb every day

113
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,319
Then stay dumb forever

114
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:41,759
Come on, come on

115
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:43,199
Those wanting to join our vinegar workshop

116
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,199
Line up over here

117
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,519
We're hiring here

118
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,360
Hurry up and come over

119
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,240
Thank you

120
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,120
Next

121
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,600
Yingrong

122
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,040
Yingrong

123
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,439
Mom, Little Sister

124
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,600
What are you doing here

125
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,160
Yingrong, let me tell you, Little Sister...

126
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,920
Yingrong

127
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:57,959
Yingrong

128
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,240
If you're hiring here

129
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,120
please consider Old Zhang and me

130
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,279
Ever since we left the factory

131
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:08,319
we haven't found stable work

132
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:09,920
Aren't you catching and selling fish

133
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,839
We can't outsell the actual fishermen

134
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,199
If there's no technical skill involved

135
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:16,439
it's not a long-term plan

136
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:18,319
But your vinegar factory is different

137
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,920
You have your own

138
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,519
unique vinegar brewing recipe

139
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,360
When competing for business

140
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,439
they won't necessarily beat you

141
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,600
My vinegar workshop is good

142
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,759
but why do I have to hire you

143
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,360
You two distorted the truth before

144
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,800
Do you think

145
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:34,839
I'm someone who forgets past grievances

146
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:35,920
Yingrong

147
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,920
You're a boss now

148
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,959
Your perspective must be different

149
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:42,240
Let's write off the past

150
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:44,040
Let's start fresh

151
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,160
Right, right, right

152
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,279
For flies with incompatible values

153
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,959
and extremely low moral standards

154
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,720
why should I have to swallow that

155
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,160
Why should I put up with this

156
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:56,160
You two go back to where you came from

157
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,519
My vinegar workshop is too small a temple

158
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,519
to accommodate two big Buddhas like you

159
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,560
Yingrong

160
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,199
Don't be like that

161
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,839
Yingrong

162
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,600
We're apologizing to you, aren't we

163
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,079
Don't just drive us away

164
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,519
Give us another chance

165
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,160
Leave

166
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,439
Yingrong

167
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,800
You really made this vinegar workshop a success

168
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,480
Of course, Mom

169
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,839
You can see it for yourself

170
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:19,519
Right now

171
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:21,519
the vinegar brewing business is booming

172
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,720
That's great

173
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,519
Since this vinegar workshop is making money

174
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:27,120
let your little sister work here

175
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,360
If she can endure hardship, that's fine

176
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,759
Then get to work

177
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,120
Come on

178
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,320
Move the grain with me

179
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,519
Move grain

180
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,159
Isn't there any easier work

181
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,000
Just come inside first

182
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,279
If you don't work now

183
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:43,720
and Xiaochuan hires someone else

184
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,000
I won't need you anymore

185
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,960
Also, change your pants next time you work

186
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,159
Yingtang

187
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,200
Be careful

188
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,519
I'll help you when I'm done

189
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,399
This is making my back ache

190
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:09,159
Who makes their own sister do hard labor

191
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,399
She doesn't act like a big sister at all

192
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:15,360
If I can get the secret recipe for brewing vinegar

193
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,519
I won't have to work anymore

194
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,240
Tang Yan

195
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,399
Tang Yan, get down here.

196
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,159
Tang Yan!

197
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,960
Hurry up.

198
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:52,200
Why did you drink so much?

199
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,320
What else is there to do?

200
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:57,039
My dad says I'm useless.

201
00:09:58,639 --> 00:09:59,200
Hey.

202
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:01,679
Why did you come find me?

203
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,720
We broke up a long time ago.

204
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,919
If I can give you the Baliang Vinegar workshop...

205
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,960
...and the secret recipe...

206
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,279
...will your dad let us be together?

207
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:14,039
You mean the one that's most popular right now?

208
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,080
Baliang Vinegar?

209
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,720
That's my Second Aunt's vinegar workshop.

210
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,159
If I have the workshop and the secret recipe...

211
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:20,080
...would you and I...

212
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,600
...be able to be our own bosses?

213
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:22,720
At that time...

214
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,879
...would you still worry about your dad looking down on you?

215
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:27,240
Don't think I don't know.

216
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,919
That vinegar workshop belongs to your second aunt.

217
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:32,080
You're actually wrong.

218
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,519
That vinegar workshop isn't Wang Yingrong's.

219
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,799
Actually, the person in charge is my dad.

220
00:10:37,519 --> 00:10:39,559
What if my dad transfers the workshop to me?

221
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,799
Right?

222
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,600
My dad taught me how to write when I was young.

223
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,919
No one in this world writes...

224
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:46,559
...more like my dad than I do.

225
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,120
Then...

226
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:55,320
If you have the secret recipe...

227
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,159
...and can help me secure the vinegar workshop...

228
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,200
...then we have a deal.

229
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,720
When that happens...

230
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,759
I'll invest in the workshop...

231
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,919
...and give you...

232
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,519
...30% of the shares.

233
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,519
How about that?

234
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:07,679
30%?

235
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:10,320
I'm giving you the workshop and the recipe.

236
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,600
That's too little.

237
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,679
If you were like me...

238
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:13,759
...and could invest money...

239
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:15,720
...I could consider giving you more shares.

240
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,679
Then I'll invest.

241
00:11:17,879 --> 00:11:20,080
You don't think I don't know...

242
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,399
...your situation?

243
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:23,080
Where would you get money to invest?

244
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:26,399
I can mortgage my house.

245
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,360
Deal.

246
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:35,120
I knew you were my darling.

247
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,600
You're the most beautiful woman in the world.

248
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:42,919
If this succeeds...

249
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,679
I'll definitely marry you.

250
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:47,519
Then my dad will approve.
